subject: U.S AMBASSADOR FUND NOTIFIC
body:
U.S AMBASSADOR FUND NOTIFICATION.
AMBASSADOR CHIMEZIE EMEKA
July 27th 11:49 A.M
U.S AMBASSADOR TO BENIN
ATTN: BENEFICIARY.
AN OFFICIAL MEETING WAS HELD WITH THE PRESIDENT OF NIGERIA/BENIN AND
MINISTER OF FINANCE CONCERNING THE UNPAID AND UNCLAIMED FUNDS TO
FOREIGN BENEFICIARIES,
I WAS VERY MUCH CONCERNED WHEN I DISCOVERED THAT YOU HAVE PAID MUCH
MONEY AND YET HAVE NOT RECEIVE YOUR FUNDS.THIS IS WHY I DECIDED TO
HELP. I WILL BE COMING
TO YOUR COUNTRY FOR AN OFFICIAL VISIT AND I WILL COME ALONG WITH YOUR
CONSIGNMENT BOX CONTAINING SUM OF $55.8 MILLION ALONG WITH ME THROUGH
UNITED STATES
DIPLOMATIC MISSION TO THE COUNTRY. BUT I WILL NOT GO THROUGH CUSTOMS
BECAUSE AS U.S AMBASSADOR TO NIGERIA /BENIN, AM A U.S GOVERNMENT AGENT
AND HAVE THE VETO
POWER TO PASS THROUGH CUSTOMS. JUST LIKE I HELPED TWO PERSONS THAT RECEIVED
THEIR FUNDS THIS YEAR 2022 THROUGH FEDEX COURIER SERVICE.
PROVEN YOU THE TRUTH, TRACK THE BELOW TRACKING NUMBERS AND CONFIRM IT:
1.)WWW.FEDEX.COMTRACKING NO: 800277347645
2.)WWW.FEDEX.COMTRACKING NO: 395659915113418
3)WWW.DHL.COMTRACKING NUMBER..7094651826.. HIS NAME IS ALPHA DIALLO...GUINEA
REPUBLIC
THEY RECEIVED THERE CONSIGNMENT BOX,WHILE MR ALPHA RECEIVED  UBA ATM
CARD.ENSURE YOU TRACK IT FIRST TO CONFIRM BY YOUR SELF AND IMMEDIATELY
AM THROUGH WITH THE MEETINGS, I SHALL THEN PROCEED TO YOUR HOME,OK.
PLEASE SEND YOUR INFORMATION AS REQUESTED BELOAW:-
1. YOUR FULL NAME
2. CELL PHONE NUMBER
3. ADDRESS WHERE YOU WANT ME TO BRING THE PACKAGE).
YOU REALLY PAID MUCH IN REGARDS OF THE DELIVERY AND THAT'S SURPRISED
ME. YOU ARE VERY LUCKY AS I SHALL BE BRINGING IT MYSELF AND NOTHING
CAN STOP ME.
YOUR PACKAGE ($55.8M) MUST BE REGISTERED AS AN AMBASSADORIAL PACKAGE
FOR ME TO DEFEAT ALL ODDS AND THE COST OF REGISTERING IT IS $75.00 THE
FEE MUST BE
PAID IN THE NEXT 50 HOURS VIA STEAM WALLET CARD SO THAT ALL NECESSARY
ARRANGEMENT CAN BE MADE BEFORE TIME WILL BE AGAINST US.
HAVE IN MIND THAT YOU HAVE ABSOLUTELY NOTHING TO FEAR OR WORRY ABOUT
OK,,, I SHALL MAKE SURE YOU RECEIVE YOUR CONSIGNMENT BOX AGAINST ALL
ODDS.. I HAVE PUT A SMILE ON MANY FACES AND YOUR LUCKY YOUR THE NEXT,,
THIS IS NOT A FLUKE OK, SO DONT HAVE A DOUBLE MIND ABOUT LOOSING YOUR
FUND OR BEEN SCAMMED,,,OK,
IF YOU FOLLOW MY INSTRUCTIONS DILIGENTLY,,YOU WILL HAVE A REASON TO
CELEBRATE THIS YEAR 2022 LIKE OTHERS,,, AND MAKE SURE YOU KEEP A
BOTTLE OF CHAMPAGN FOR ME WHEN I ARRIVE AND A CIGAR TOO..
AS SOON AS YOU SEND THE FEE $75.I SHALL SEND MY FLIGHT SCHEDULE TO YOU
TRULY,
AMBASSADOR CHIMEZIE
U.S AMBASSADOR TO BENIN

subject: Re:    U.S AMBASSADOR FUND NOTIFIC
body:
Dear Ambassador Chimezie Emeka,

Thank you for your email and the information provided. I am indeed surprised to hear about this unclaimed fund. However, I would like to clarify a few things before we proceed.

Firstly, could you please provide more details about the origin of these funds? How did my name come up in connection with them?

Secondly, I understand that you will be bringing the package personally, but I would like to know more about the registration process of an ambassadorial package and why there is a fee involved.

Lastly, could you please provide some form of official documentation or proof regarding this matter? This is simply for my personal records and assurance.

I look forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Betty
